# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ DECONSTRUCTION
  inputs : crafted-item вҠ— CraftLineage<Vec<MaterialId>> В· tool вҲҲ {Voidsmelter|Soulhammer|Phaseloom} В· skill В· workshop
  tool-affinity :
    Voidsmelter вҶҰ metals + gems     В· base 0.45
    Soulhammer  вҶҰ jewelry + woods   В· base 0.50
    Phaseloom   вҶҰ cloths + leathers В· base 0.55
  recover-fn : raw = base + 0.4Г—(skill/100) + 0.2Г—(tool_q/100) ; clamp вҲҲ [0.30, 0.70]
                вҖј NEVER 0% (no flat-zero return)
  outputs : mats Г— recover_fraction В· 50% glyph-fragment-drop В· item-consumed В· tool -1 dura
  costs   : workshop-time = tier Г— 5s base (skill -вүӨ50%) В· tool-dura -1 (legendary -0.5)
  audit   : Audit<"deconstruct", item-id, mats-returned, glyph-drop?>

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ ALCHEMY  (potion-brew + transmutation)

  В§ POTION-BREW  (additive)
    inputs : Vial[T1] + 1..3 reagents (catalyst optional)
    duration : 10s base В· -2s per skill-tier
    failure  : skill < required вҮ’ 50% bottle-explodes (lose-mats В· audit-emit)

  В§ TRANSMUTATION  (multiplicative В· "lead-to-gold")
    rule : 3-of-tier-N + catalyst вҶ’ 1-of-tier-(N+1) В· probabilistic
    base-success : 0.20 + 0.005Г—skill        # skill 0=20% В· skill 100=70%
    catalysts (single-use В· consumed-on-attempt) :
      Voidessence  1.5Г— В· Soulflux 2.0Г— В· Catalystgem 1.3Г—
      Voidessence + Soulflux вҮ’ stack 3.0Г— В· clamp вүӨ 0.95
    skill-gate : transmute-skill вүҘ 20Г—N (target-tier)
    failure    : on-fail вҮ’ 1-of-tier-N preserved (others-consumed) В· audit-emit
    forbidden  : В¬ transmute consumables вҶ” equipment (cross-category-block)

  В§ WORKSHOP-REQUIREMENT
    must-be-in workshop-zone with AlchemyTable affordance
    ConsentZone : N/A (workshop = neutral В· В¬ thematic-gate)

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ SKILL-SCALING  (quality-tier-shift В¬ damage-multiplier)

  В§ AXES  (separate)
    craft-skill В· deconstruct-skill В· alchemy-skill В· enchant-skill   (each 0..100)

  В§ XP-CURVE (diminishing)
    fn xp_gain(action_tier, current_skill) -> u32
      base = action_tier Г— 10 ; dim = 1 + skill/25 ; result = base/dim
    threshold : 100 Г— (skill+1)ВІ

  В§ QUALITY-TIERS  (6 В· output-side-only)
    Q1 Common      Г—1.00  В· 0 slot
    Q2 Fine        Г—1.10  В· 0..1 slots
    Q3 Superior    Г—1.20  В· 1..2 slots
    Q4 Master      Г—1.30  В· 2..3 slots
    Q5 Heroic      Г—1.40  В· 3 slots + named-author
    Q6 Legendary   Г—1.50  В· 3 slots + lineage-recorded + Audit<"legendary-craft", Пү-step>

  В§ THRESHOLDS  (P of next-tier В· roll-down on miss В· В¬ flat-fail)
    skill вүҘ 0   вҮ’ Common (always)
    skill вүҘ 20  вҮ’ Fine        P 0.30
    skill вүҘ 40  вҮ’ Superior    P 0.25
    skill вүҘ 60  вҮ’ Master      P 0.20
    skill вүҘ 80  вҮ’ Heroic      P 0.15
    skill вүҘ 100 вҮ’ Legendary   P 0.10

  В§ INVARIANT  вҖј  stat-multiplier вүӨ 1.50 (anti-power-creep)
    higher-skill вү  raw-damage-up В· only-tier-shift
    glyph-affixes = actual-build-shape (per В§ GLYPH-SLOTS)

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ GLYPH-SLOTS  (item-customization layer)
  capacity : 0..3 per item В· per-quality (see В§ QUALITY-TIERS)
  glyph    : consumable-fragment В· inserted-once В· grants-affix
  sources  : deconstruct 50%-drop В· transmute-fail 30%-drop В· workshop-discovery В· В¬ purchasable
  affixes  (sample В· post-MVP-extensible) :
    A-fire +10% fire-dmg В· A-frost +10% frost В· A-life +20 HP В· A-mana +20 MP
    A-haste +5% action-speed В· A-resist-X +15% В· A-thorns reflect 5%
    A-soulward +1 ConsentZone-grace
  deconstruct-of-slotted : 50%-chance recover-glyph-as-shard В· 3 shards = 1 glyph at workshop

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ WORKSHOPS  (procgen via cssl-host-procgen-rooms)
  Z-forge       : weapons + armor + jewelry  (anvil + furnace)
  Z-alchemy-lab : potion-brew + transmute    (cauldron + alchemy-table)
  Z-enchant     : glyph-slot operations      (rune-circle)
  Z-loom        : cloth-weave + leather-work (spidersilk-loom)
  invariant : layout deterministic-per (floor-seed Г— zone-id) вҮ’ replayable

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ FAB-PROCGEN-INTEGRATION  (consumes substrate)
  cssl-host-fab-procgen   : material-instance gen (color/texture/tag)
                            e.g. IronвҶ’{#6B6B6B,"metal-rough","iron"} В· VoidsteelвҶ’{phase-shift,"void-fractal","voidsteel"}
                            higher-skill вҮ’ deterministic-best-roll on-grain
  cssl-host-procgen-rooms : workshop-zone procgen (Z-forge/lab/enchant/loom)

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ SUBSTRATE-CONSUMPTION  (downstream-PODs)
  cssl-host-craft-graph  (POD-2-B3 В· NEW)
    surface :
      pub fn evaluate_recipe(graph : &RecipeGraph, recipe : RecipeId, mats : &MatPool) -> CraftResult
      pub fn deconstruct(item : &CraftedItem, tool : DeconstructTool, skill : u8) -> DeconstructResult
      pub fn transmute(inputs : &[MaterialId], catalyst : Option<MaterialId>, skill : u8) -> TransmuteResult
      pub fn brew(recipe : RecipeId, reagents : &[MaterialId], skill : u8) -> BrewResult
      pub fn quality_roll(skill : u8, recipe_tier : u8, rng : &mut DetRng) -> QualityTier
    constraints : pure-functional В· вүӨ 1200 LOC В· вүҘ 20 tests
    determinism : seeded-DetRng input вҮ’ bit-exact-output
  cssl-host-fab-procgen     : material-instance gen
  cssl-host-procgen-rooms   : workshop zones
  cssl-host-attestation     : per-craft Audit (anti-cheat anchor)
  cssl-host-causal-seed     : crafted-items as DAG-nodes (legendary-lineage)

