В§ BALANCE-METRICS  (target-shape В· post-content-validate)
  M-1 craft-engagement     вүҘ 40% players past-floor-3 use craft
  M-2 deconstruct-recovery curve 30%..70% Г— (skill Г— tool-q) В· NEVER 0%
  M-3 alchemy-uniqueness   вүҘ 200 viable potion-recipes (combinatorial-space)
  M-4 transmute-curve      skill 0=20% В· skill 100=70% pre-catalyst
  M-5 quality-distrib.     skill-100 player вҮ’ Heroic+ вүҘ 60% of crafts
  M-6 audit-coverage       100% crafts emit Audit В· 0 silent-craft

# в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ

В§ FAILURE-MODES  (handled В· В¬ silent)
  F-1 recipe-gap        missing-ingredient вҮ’ UI-prompt + alternate-suggest
  F-2 dup-exploit       Audit-emit + checkpoint-rollback (cssl-host-attestation)
  F-3 skill-overflow    skill clamped вҲҲ [0,100] В· audit-emit on attempt
  F-4 tool-broken       tool-q вүӨ 0 вҮ’ deconstruct-blocked + UI-prompt
  F-5 transmute-fail    audit-emit В· 1-of-tier-N preserved (В¬ total-loss)
  F-6 brew-explosion    skill < req-50% вҮ’ mats-lost (consent-zone N/A)
  F-7 lineage-corrupt   missing CraftLineage вҮ’ fallback to base-recovery

